                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yankchina/">杨安康</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-10-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">细致的分析，完全的视角</p>
        </div>
